list.abstract: Resistance，英语单词，主要用作名词，意思是阻力；电阻；抵抗；反抗；抵抗力。
抵抗组织（Resistance，是星球大战中的虚拟组织，旧译：抵抗力量）是由莱娅·奥加纳（Leia Organa）组建的相对独立在新共和国的军事抵抗运动（Military resistance movement）。 本组织原旨在为可能到来的战争做准备，第一秩序（First Order）崛起后，抵抗组织专门针对第一秩序。

yingyinNormal.en: It turned the last of my guards against me. There was no resistance left inside the Capitol or the mansion.
yingyinNormal.zh: 最后连忠于我的卫兵也倒戈了，国会区和总统府里都没人反抗了。
所以你是抵抗组织的人？

yingyinNormal.en: I've never met a Resistance fighter before.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我之前从没见过抵抗组织的战士。

yingyinNormal.en: You had resistance even when the Democrats controlled the House.
yingyinNormal.zh: 即便是民主党控制国会时，你也遭遇了阻力。

yingyinNormal.en: Obviously. Yes, I am. I'm with the Resistance, yeah. I am with the Resistance.
yingyinNormal.zh: 显而易见，没错，我是抵抗组织的人，对，我是抵抗组织的一员。

yingyinNormal.en: Sooner or later, the pests evolve resistance to every new product.
yingyinNormal.zh: 迟早这些昆虫能进化出对任何新产品的免疫能力。

yingyinNormal.en: Russian and Chinese troops are now moving across Europe. Without resistance.
yingyinNormal.zh: 俄国和中国的军队正在横扫欧洲，一路所向披靡。

yingyinNormal.en: I don't speak that. All right, between us, I'm not with the Resistance, okay?
yingyinNormal.zh: 我不会说你这门语言，好吧，我只告诉你我不是抵抗组织的人，好吧？

yingyinNormal.en: The First Order wants the map. Finn is with the Resistance. I'm just a scavenger.
yingyinNormal.zh: 第一秩序想要那张地图，芬恩是抵抗组织成员，我只是一个拾荒者。

yingyinNormal.en: You're with the Resistance? What? No, no, no. I'm breaking you out. Can you fly a TIE fighter?
yingyinNormal.zh: 你是抵抗组织成员吗？什么？不是，我只是来帮你逃出去，你会驾驶TIE战斗机吗？

yingyinNormal.en: BB-8 said the location of the Resistance base is need to know. If I'm taking you there, I need to know.
yingyinNormal.zh: BB-8说抵抗组织基地的位置只有内部人员知道，如果我要带你们去那的话，我需要知道那个地点。

yingyinNormal.en: It feels nicer and you can feel more resistance in there. That can go into a bowl now and sit and rest.
yingyinNormal.zh: 现在就好很多了，你能感觉出来，更筋道，现在可以放到碗里，然后休息一会。

yingyinNormal.en: This droid has to get to the Resistance base as soon as possible. He's carrying a map to Luke Skywalker.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这个机器人必须尽快赶到抵抗组织基地，他携带着一份通向卢克·天行者所在地的地图。

yingyinNormal.en: By the time the ship's going fast enough for air resistance to matter, it'll be high enough that there's practically no air.
yingyinNormal.zh: 等到飞船的速度快到会受空气阻力影响的时候，就应该已经到达没有多少空气的高度了。

yingyinNormal.en: For the piece de resistance. Seriously? Look at those! Lucky pants! What girl can feel so lucky in a pair of pants like these.
yingyinNormal.zh: 现在才是主菜。不会吧？看看这个!好运内裤。哪个女孩穿上这样的内裤觉得会有好运啊。

yingyinNormal.en: Things have been going really well with the infinite resistance gyroscope. That's great. How so? Oh, the project is classified. I can't tell you.
yingyinNormal.zh: 最近我们研发无限持续陀螺仪很顺利呢。那很好啊，怎么顺利？这个项目是机密。恕我不能透露。

yingyinNormal.en: So, she's now falling from 290 feet, instead of 300 feet, reaching the speed of 173 feet per second just before impact, not counting air resistance.
yingyinNormal.zh: 等于她现在是从290英尺落下，而不是300英尺，这样她在落地时的速度可以达到173英尺每秒，不考虑空气阻力的话。

yingyinNormal.en: Which leaves 470 beverages which have extremely high unhealthy levels of calories. Consuming large amounts of rapidly digested sugar and high fructose corn syrup causes a spike in blood sugar and insulin, which can lead to inflammation and insulin resistance.
yingyinNormal.zh: 470种饮料，含有极高且不健康的卡路里消化如此大量的可快速消化的糖与高果糖浆会造成血糖在短时间飙升与触发胰岛素的大量释放，进而导致发炎反应与胰岛素抵抗等现象。
